msgstr "On the Side"

msgid "Private Tutor & Cram School Instructor"
msgstr "個別指導講師 / 塾講師"

msgid "English & Social Studies, junior-high students"
msgstr "中学生向け 英語・社会"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"Outside work, I teach English and social studies to junior-high students at "
"a local cram school (<a href=\"%(cram_url)s\" target=\"_blank\" "
"rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"work-link\">CER</a>). The distance from "
"enterprise sales to thirteen-year-olds is shorter than it sounds — both ask "
"you to read the room, slow down when it matters, and believe the person in "
"front of you can go further than they think they can."
msgstr ""
"本業のかたわら、地元の塾（<a href=\"%(cram_url)s\" target=\"_blank\" "
"rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"work-link\">CER</a>）で中学生に英語と社会"
"を教えています。エンタープライズ営業と13歳の生徒との距離は、思っているほど遠"
"くありません。どちらも、相手の空気を読み、要所では立ち止まり、目の前の相手が"
"自分で思っている以上に成長できると信じる — その姿勢が問われる仕事だと感じてい"
"ます。"

